1
00:01:42,190 --> 00:01:45,190
Run for Young

2
00:01:46,810 --> 00:01:47,490
Big Mouth.

3
00:01:47,490 --> 00:01:48,490
What shall we eat today?

4
00:01:49,090 --> 00:01:50,250
Spicy Noodles.

5
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:52,610
No. I want to have hot pot!

6
00:01:52,610 --> 00:01:53,330
Which restaurant?

7
00:01:56,050 --> 00:01:56,930
What are they doing?

8
00:01:56,930 --> 00:01:57,530
I don't know.

9
00:02:00,090 --> 00:02:01,930
Bro, what are you doing?

10
00:02:02,490 --> 00:02:03,850
Artistic creation.

11
00:02:03,970 --> 00:02:04,850
What kind?

12
00:02:04,850 --> 00:02:05,810
Filmmaking.

13
00:02:06,130 --> 00:02:07,370
What film?

14
00:02:07,370 --> 00:02:09,090
"Curiosity Kills the Cat"

15
00:02:09,090 --> 00:02:10,570
This name is "good".

16
00:02:10,930 --> 00:02:11,970
What's wrong with it?

17
00:02:11,970 --> 00:02:13,130
People'll protest against it

18
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:13,850
a dozen years later.

19
00:02:13,850 --> 00:02:14,850
- Yeah! - Why?

20
00:02:14,850 --> 00:02:17,410
By that time the world will be full of ailurophiles.

21
00:02:17,410 --> 00:02:18,610
How dare you kill a cat?

22
00:02:19,410 --> 00:02:22,250
You've a way with words, young man.

23
00:02:22,250 --> 00:02:23,290
What name should I use then?

24
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:25,330
What name?

25
00:02:27,330 --> 00:02:29,730
Manual of Classy Movie Names.

26
00:02:29,730 --> 00:02:30,970
One day,

27
00:02:31,010 --> 00:02:32,770
you will be the pioneer of youth films.

28
00:02:32,770 --> 00:02:34,010
Seriously?

29
00:02:34,010 --> 00:02:34,970
One day,

30
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:36,330
you will make Chongqing

31
00:02:36,330 --> 00:02:37,450
a city visited by a lot of Internet celebrities.

32
00:02:37,730 --> 00:02:38,810
Really?

33
00:02:38,810 --> 00:02:39,690
One day,

34
00:02:40,090 --> 00:02:41,970
you will be the pride of Chongqing!

35
00:02:41,970 --> 00:02:42,970
Impossible!

36
00:02:43,050 --> 00:02:43,770
You will!

37
00:02:44,730 --> 00:02:45,610
As long as you buy

38
00:02:46,250 --> 00:02:47,930
this Manual of Classy Movie Names.

39
00:02:48,050 --> 00:02:48,650
It's 50 yuan.

40
00:02:50,370 --> 00:02:51,690
Judging from your school uniform,

41
00:02:53,090 --> 00:02:54,650
we're alumni,

42
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:55,610
I believe you.

43
00:02:58,570 --> 00:03:00,810
The way ahead is long.

44
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:03,930
I shall search heaven and earth.

45
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:06,450
Shadow Over Shanghai.

46
00:03:07,050 --> 00:03:08,250
Lost, Indulgence.

47
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:09,690
Fleet of Time.

48
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:13,810
I Belonged to You.

49
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:21,310
Episode 13 How Come You Don't Know?

50
00:03:29,850 --> 00:03:30,850
Screaming Glasses Noodles

51
00:03:30,850 --> 00:03:32,490
Are you Zhu Weijiao's father?

52
00:03:34,330 --> 00:03:34,950
And you are?

53
00:03:35,450 --> 00:03:37,090
I am the parent of her classmate.

54
00:03:38,410 --> 00:03:39,810
That handsome classmate

55
00:03:39,810 --> 00:03:41,050
called Ma...

56
00:03:41,050 --> 00:03:43,250
Do you know Ma Tian and your daughter

57
00:03:43,290 --> 00:03:44,290
spent a day in Chengdu

58
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:45,690
and stayed out all night?

59
00:03:46,850 --> 00:03:48,570
They went with several classmates.

60
00:03:49,570 --> 00:03:51,210
Young people seek fun. I understand it.

61
00:03:51,810 --> 00:03:53,090
But as a parent, I don't think

62
00:03:53,130 --> 00:03:54,050
this is right.

63
00:03:54,970 --> 00:03:57,130
At their age, they have their own ideas.

64
00:03:57,130 --> 00:03:58,050
But now,

65
00:03:58,050 --> 00:04:00,330
they lack self-control.

66
00:04:02,130 --> 00:04:03,970
You should believe in your son.

67
00:04:06,850 --> 00:04:07,770
Mr. Zhu.

68
00:04:08,570 --> 00:04:10,650
I'll just make myself clear.

69
00:04:11,850 --> 00:04:13,890
I don't want anyone

70
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:15,650
to affect Ma Tian's study

71
00:04:15,650 --> 00:04:17,690
in this critical time,

72
00:04:18,250 --> 00:04:19,610
including your daughter.

73
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,230
Got it.

74
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:26,750
Got it.

75
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:28,810
Fine.

76
00:04:31,770 --> 00:04:32,570
Do you want noodles?

77
00:04:49,170 --> 00:04:50,930
Whose cute

78
00:04:50,930 --> 00:04:52,450
daughter

79
00:04:52,450 --> 00:04:53,330
pulls a long face?

80
00:04:54,690 --> 00:04:55,730
Yours.

81
00:04:59,610 --> 00:05:00,250
Don't cry.

82
00:05:01,370 --> 00:05:02,810
Dad, I'm sorry.

83
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:05,530
Don't say that.

84
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:09,610
It's fine.

85
00:05:21,370 --> 00:05:23,170
No big deal. We won't hang out with them!

86
00:05:24,690 --> 00:05:25,450
Right.

87
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:27,850
Don't even talk

88
00:05:28,210 --> 00:05:28,970
to these rich people!

89
00:05:29,210 --> 00:05:29,850
Yes!

90
00:05:29,850 --> 00:05:30,770
They're rich, so what?

91
00:05:31,170 --> 00:05:32,050
So what!

92
00:05:32,050 --> 00:05:32,670
Eat noodles.

93
00:05:33,610 --> 00:05:34,930
I want a big bowl.

94
00:05:35,130 --> 00:05:35,730
Sure.

95
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:38,250
I really want to eat noodles now.

96
00:05:41,410 --> 00:05:42,130
Good.

97
00:05:42,130 --> 00:05:42,730
Eat as much as you like.

98
00:05:45,210 --> 00:05:47,050
Dad cooks the best noodles in the world.

99
00:05:47,930 --> 00:05:48,610
I know.

100
00:05:52,130 --> 00:05:52,970
What is this?

101
00:05:52,970 --> 00:05:54,210
This is crispy chestnut cake.

102
00:05:54,210 --> 00:05:55,170
We're having this today.

103
00:05:55,170 --> 00:05:55,890
We'll eat that tomorrow.

104
00:05:58,950 --> 00:05:59,570
Here.

105
00:06:01,010 --> 00:06:01,650
Is it delicious?

106
00:06:03,730 --> 00:06:04,570
So yummy.

107
00:06:04,570 --> 00:06:06,090
That's enough.

108
00:06:07,690 --> 00:06:08,450
What's the matter?

109
00:06:09,730 --> 00:06:11,090
You stole my deskmate!

110
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:12,930
What?

111
00:06:13,410 --> 00:06:15,170
You gave me up, saying you're studying for the NCEE!

112
00:06:17,250 --> 00:06:17,870
Ignore him.

113
00:06:26,290 --> 00:06:27,490
W-what are you calculating?

114
00:06:30,930 --> 00:06:31,850
I'm calculating

115
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,410
the distance from Chongqing to the UK.

116
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:38,970
Look.

117
00:06:40,210 --> 00:06:41,210
I measured it.

118
00:06:42,250 --> 00:06:43,930
The distance from Chongqing to the UK

119
00:06:43,930 --> 00:06:45,570
is ten centimeters on the map.

120
00:06:45,610 --> 00:06:48,290
The scale is 1:90 million.

121
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:50,730
Ten multiplies 90 million is 900 million.

122
00:06:50,730 --> 00:06:52,650
900 million centimeters equals 9,000 kilometers.

123
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:57,690
How's it? Amazing, huh?

124
00:06:58,650 --> 00:06:59,410
You made great progress.

125
00:07:06,850 --> 00:07:08,010
When I was a child,

126
00:07:09,610 --> 00:07:11,170
I thought the long stairs in Daxing Village

127
00:07:11,890 --> 00:07:13,170
were long.

128
00:07:25,410 --> 00:07:26,010
And then?

129
00:07:30,250 --> 00:07:30,870
And then,

130
00:07:33,890 --> 00:07:34,690
I know what real distance is.

131
00:07:35,770 --> 00:07:36,930
I got it just now.

132
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:58,890
Jiao.

133
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:02,830
Jiao.

134
00:08:09,410 --> 00:08:10,130
What's wrong?

135
00:08:12,410 --> 00:08:13,010
Jiao.

136
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:14,130
Look at me.

137
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:36,610
Jiao, what's wrong with you?

138
00:08:36,610 --> 00:08:38,530
You guys! Something happened to her!

139
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:46,569
Jiao, this is my seat.

140
00:08:48,169 --> 00:08:48,770
You take my seat.

141
00:08:48,950 --> 00:08:49,590
Why?

142
00:08:50,809 --> 00:08:51,650
Why what?

143
00:08:51,650 --> 00:08:52,610
Can you do it?

144
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:54,450
Yes.

145
00:08:54,530 --> 00:08:55,169
Yes.

146
00:08:55,370 --> 00:08:56,730
All right, class.

147
00:08:56,730 --> 00:08:58,570
Now you start filling out the application form.

148
00:08:59,490 --> 00:09:02,290
I believe some people know exactly where they want to go

149
00:09:02,290 --> 00:09:02,890
and where they can go.

150
00:09:03,490 --> 00:09:05,970
But some people are still confused now, right?

151
00:09:06,410 --> 00:09:07,410
It's normal.

152
00:09:08,210 --> 00:09:10,370
Because you're making your last choices

153
00:09:10,370 --> 00:09:11,770
in high school.

154
00:09:11,770 --> 00:09:13,050
Please take it seriously.

155
00:09:13,050 --> 00:09:13,770
Come on, everybody.

156
00:09:15,330 --> 00:09:17,930
You should think it through before you fill in the form.

157
00:09:18,570 --> 00:09:20,650
We all know that NCEE is very important.

158
00:09:20,890 --> 00:09:23,170
But the application is also very important.

159
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:28,250
Ma Tian.

160
00:09:28,770 --> 00:09:30,530
I know you're a model student.

161
00:09:30,530 --> 00:09:31,810
But please don't hold your head

162
00:09:31,810 --> 00:09:33,090
high all the time.

163
00:09:35,370 --> 00:09:36,490
No, teacher.

164
00:09:36,690 --> 00:09:37,570
My nose is bleeding.

165
00:09:42,630 --> 00:09:43,230
Yuanyuan.

166
00:09:43,730 --> 00:09:46,130
Let's choose colleges in Chongqing.

167
00:09:47,330 --> 00:09:48,050
Why not?

168
00:09:52,570 --> 00:09:53,190
What do you choose?

169
00:09:55,010 --> 00:09:57,010
I just filled it out for the sake of filling itself.

170
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:58,210
Why don't you show me?

171
00:09:58,330 --> 00:09:58,970
No!

172
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:00,890
You're not my deskmate anymore.

173
00:10:01,090 --> 00:10:01,810
Leave me alone.

174
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:04,410
Why should I show you?

175
00:10:06,330 --> 00:10:07,370
You're a man!

176
00:10:08,370 --> 00:10:09,450
So petty.

177
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:11,050
Yuanyuan, let's fill it out carefully.

178
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:18,790
Tsinghua University

179
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:29,970
Have you filled it out?

180
00:10:31,770 --> 00:10:32,410
Almost done.

181
00:10:36,570 --> 00:10:37,610
I've filled it out for you.

182
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:42,990
Southwest Sports College

183
00:10:45,210 --> 00:10:46,050
Will I get admitted?

184
00:10:46,490 --> 00:10:47,290
Rest assured.

185
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:48,570
As long as you work hard.

186
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:51,730
So you won't fill it out?

187
00:10:52,130 --> 00:10:53,450
Why do I fill it?

188
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:54,250
I will study abroad.

189
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:06,250
Let me help you.

190
00:11:06,250 --> 00:11:06,930
Leave me alone.

191
00:11:08,410 --> 00:11:09,010
It's critical, yet you...

192
00:11:09,970 --> 00:11:11,010
Leave me alone!

193
00:11:20,490 --> 00:11:21,490
What the hell is going on?

194
00:11:22,650 --> 00:11:24,010
How do I know?

195
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:25,530
You must have offended Hercules Jiao.

196
00:11:25,530 --> 00:11:27,090
That's why she separated us.

197
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:28,410
I'm supposed to be sitting with Anran.

198
00:11:28,410 --> 00:11:29,290
And now?

199
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:36,890
It's because of me?

200
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:54,450
Bro,

201
00:11:54,610 --> 00:11:56,010
your forhead looks dark.

202
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,410
Something big must have happened.

203
00:12:00,250 --> 00:12:02,530
Could it be that Jiao caused it?

204
00:12:02,850 --> 00:12:04,890
Yeah, Jiao, tell him what's wrong with you.

205
00:12:05,690 --> 00:12:07,010
Yeah, what's wrong with you?

206
00:12:09,970 --> 00:12:11,490
Don't come and talk to me anymore.

207
00:12:13,610 --> 00:12:14,210
Why?

208
00:12:14,210 --> 00:12:15,170
There is no reason.

209
00:12:17,010 --> 00:12:20,250
Is it because I made fun of you in the classroom?

210
00:12:20,690 --> 00:12:21,730
I was just kidding.

211
00:12:23,050 --> 00:12:24,610
Why are you like Doggo?

212
00:12:24,610 --> 00:12:25,850
Silly!

213
00:12:25,850 --> 00:12:27,010
Do you think you're cute?

214
00:12:27,170 --> 00:12:27,970
Am I cute?

215
00:12:28,730 --> 00:12:29,930
NCEE is drawing near.

216
00:12:30,090 --> 00:12:31,290
I dare not affect you.

217
00:12:32,050 --> 00:12:33,570
Or we'll be blamed again.

218
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:36,610
You go your way,

219
00:12:36,610 --> 00:12:37,930
and I'll go mine.

220
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:49,250
Why don't you go home

221
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:50,050
and ask your mother?

222
00:12:56,010 --> 00:12:56,650
Mom.

223
00:12:57,450 --> 00:12:58,450
I want to ask you something.

224
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:00,010
Go ahead.

225
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:04,730
A close female classmate of mine

226
00:13:04,730 --> 00:13:05,810
stopped talking to me suddenly.

227
00:13:06,730 --> 00:13:08,050
I want to know

228
00:13:08,050 --> 00:13:09,730
if you have talked to her or done something?

229
00:13:13,530 --> 00:13:14,570
I went to her father.

230
00:13:14,570 --> 00:13:15,290
What did you say?

231
00:13:17,010 --> 00:13:18,050
I was blunt.

232
00:13:18,650 --> 00:13:19,850
I said I didn't want his daughter

233
00:13:19,890 --> 00:13:21,210
to affect you.

234
00:13:21,210 --> 00:13:22,250
What did she do?

235
00:13:23,210 --> 00:13:24,450
Do you think

236
00:13:24,450 --> 00:13:26,690
what kind of future will you have with her?

237
00:13:27,810 --> 00:13:29,530
Even if she can get into college,

238
00:13:30,330 --> 00:13:32,050
can you two be admitted to the same university?

239
00:13:33,770 --> 00:13:35,770
You will go to Peking University or Tsinghua University.

240
00:13:36,810 --> 00:13:39,050
If you don't let go of each other,

241
00:13:39,210 --> 00:13:42,130
you are both being irresponsible to each other.

242
00:13:43,530 --> 00:13:44,530
You definitely won't

243
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:46,530
have a happy ending.

244
00:13:46,890 --> 00:13:48,250
How do you know?

245
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:52,770
Honey,

246
00:13:53,610 --> 00:13:55,410
what do we usually do?

247
00:13:56,170 --> 00:13:57,810
We do a lot of things.

248
00:13:58,850 --> 00:13:59,930
We

249
00:14:00,490 --> 00:14:01,290
read novels,

250
00:14:01,330 --> 00:14:02,170
watch plays,

251
00:14:02,210 --> 00:14:03,730
eat ice candies

252
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:05,850
and do break dancing together.

253
00:14:06,730 --> 00:14:07,410
Look.

254
00:14:08,210 --> 00:14:09,130
What do you think

255
00:14:09,730 --> 00:14:11,250
you have to support

256
00:14:11,250 --> 00:14:12,650
your relationship in the long run?

257
00:14:15,490 --> 00:14:16,490
Our love for each other.

258
00:14:18,890 --> 00:14:19,690
This is one of them.

259
00:14:21,130 --> 00:14:22,930
But in the long run,

260
00:14:23,730 --> 00:14:26,370
it's more about common hobbies

261
00:14:26,610 --> 00:14:27,890
and common topics.

262
00:14:29,890 --> 00:14:31,290
Do you think you

263
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:33,330
have any common topics?

264
00:14:35,050 --> 00:14:36,570
Can you always have them?

265
00:14:37,850 --> 00:14:40,330
Do you have anything in common with her?

266
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:42,850
You take

267
00:14:43,810 --> 00:14:45,210
a momentary hormonal impulse

268
00:14:45,730 --> 00:14:46,770
as love.

269
00:14:47,890 --> 00:14:49,090
But I want to ask you

270
00:14:49,850 --> 00:14:51,050
can you take responsibility

271
00:14:51,170 --> 00:14:52,890
for her future?

272
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:57,010
Since you can't answer

273
00:14:57,530 --> 00:14:58,730
all these questions,

274
00:14:59,930 --> 00:15:02,130
why do you intrude in her life?

275
00:15:05,370 --> 00:15:06,490
But if she were

276
00:15:06,490 --> 00:15:07,610
Anran,

277
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:10,130
would you say these to me?

278
00:15:10,570 --> 00:15:11,170
Well.

279
00:15:11,490 --> 00:15:13,330
We have watched Anran grow up.

280
00:15:14,450 --> 00:15:16,570
You and her share similar

281
00:15:16,570 --> 00:15:18,290
living environment and education.

282
00:15:19,290 --> 00:15:20,010
After all,

283
00:15:20,610 --> 00:15:22,290
I know nothing about the family

284
00:15:22,930 --> 00:15:24,090
who sells noodles.

285
00:15:26,530 --> 00:15:27,370
To put it simply,

286
00:15:27,850 --> 00:15:29,090
this is your prejudice!

287
00:15:36,850 --> 00:15:37,490
Luo Shenxi!

288
00:15:38,050 --> 00:15:39,970
I have read the application you filled.

289
00:15:43,370 --> 00:15:44,650
What's wrong with it?

290
00:15:45,850 --> 00:15:46,890
Your application.

291
00:15:47,410 --> 00:15:48,210
Is it possible?

292
00:15:49,490 --> 00:15:50,290
Do you know

293
00:15:50,570 --> 00:15:52,410
this is very serious.

294
00:15:52,770 --> 00:15:54,290
Stop messing around!

295
00:15:55,650 --> 00:15:56,770
